videos.description: Trevor Lawrence throws a beautiful back-shoulder pass to Justyn Ross, who hauls it in and crosses the goal line to extend the Tigers' lead to 14-6.
videos.headline: Lawrence tosses 19-yard TD before halftime

videos.description: Travis Etienne slips through a tackle and breaks into the open field, getting to the end zone to make it 28-6 Clemson.
videos.headline: Etienne goes 29 yards for 2nd TD of night

videos.description: Trevor Lawrence rolls to his right and puts it up high for T.J. Chase, who goes airborne to bring it down in the end zone and make it 35-6 Tigers.
videos.headline: Lawrence connects with Chase for 10-yard TD pass
